	<p>Tried to go for my first trial group, guildie cleric invited me, and I got there, asked for some mage summoned focus items form a nearby Cleric, got KEI and waited... and waited.. and waited... <br />
<br />
Cleric disbanded and I asked if he still doing trials with us, he said he was getting rest of group... I wait... and wait... and wait... (I'm extremely impatient <img src="images/smilies/wink.gif" border="0" alt="" title="wink" smilieid="5" /> )<br />
<br />
Cleric comes back with a Chanter, Wiz, and a bunch of Melee...<br />
<br />
He says he wants me to buff them... I realized that I was pimped out of buffs, by a guildie...  I gate out after buffing with Focus, STA, and AGI, log out with sour taste in my mouth.<br />
<br />
Been trying for trials lately, and all I get are people asking me to buff them... what did you guys do?<br />
<br />
And how do you respond to buff beggars?  (Just as a little poll)</p>
	
	
	
	
	
