	<p>When sitting in the trials room LFG...<br />
<br />
and someone asks you for buffs for their group just say:<br />
<br />
My buffs are part of what I add to a group. If you'd like my buffs, please group me for a trial run. <img src="images/smilies/biggrin.gif" border="0" alt="" title="big grin" smilieid="4" /> <br />
<br />
............<br />
I can see zero point in buffing a group you're not in, increasing their chances for sucess, which means you get to wait for the trial to reset.<br />
<br />
To help get through the trials, make Damage Shield potions. They do add an extra edge.<br />
When my group won, we had a chanter in the group with project illusion, so we all went in as fire elementals, with Shammie DS, with Chanter DS.<br />
(Just remember to click off the illusion before leaving the trial staging area, the guards outside don't like elementals)</p>
	
	
	
